{"id":5747,"date":"2020-11-18T12:43:32","date_gmt":"2020-11-18T05:43:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/?p=5747"},"modified":"2021-03-26T10:46:59","modified_gmt":"2021-03-26T03:46:59","slug":"mot-so-cach-chon-rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/mot-so-cach-chon-rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu.html","title":{"rendered":"M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn r\u00e8m c\u1eeda \u0111\u1eb9p cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong><em>Trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n hi\u1ec7n nay, ai c\u0169ng mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 th\u1eadt tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi s\u1edf th\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c d\u00e0i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u01a1i t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m sau. V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u00e3y t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian th\u1eadt l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh mu\u1ed1n chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn r\u00e8m c\u1eeda \u0111\u1eb9p cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7, gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn r\u00e8m c\u1eeda cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5750\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-600x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"788\" height=\"525\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-510x340.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 788px) 100vw, 788px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000080;\"><strong>Nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc ch\u1ecdn r\u00e8m c\u1eeda \u0111\u1eb9p cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Ch\u1ecdn r\u00e8m c\u1eeda theo m\u00e0u s\u01a1n t\u01b0\u1eddng<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u1ecdn r\u00e8m theo m\u00f9a<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u1ecdn r\u00e8m theo phong th\u1ee7y (tu\u1ed5i, m\u1ec7nh, s\u1edf th\u00edch,&#8230;)<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u1ecdn theo ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000080;\"><strong>C\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn r\u00e8m c\u1eeda \u0111\u1eb9p cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #800080;\"><strong>Theo \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1eafn s\u00e1ng (c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng)<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ri\u00eang t\u01b0 n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c che ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. C\u1ea3 bu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0a v\u00e0 bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i, n\u1ebfu r\u00e8m c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 kh\u00f4ng che \u0111\u1ee7 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 s\u00e2u. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f9y v\u00e0o s\u1edf th\u00edch c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m t\u1eeb 80% &#8211; 100%<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5752\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-1-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"525\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-1-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-1-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-1-510x383.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-1.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #800080;\"><strong>M\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Khi ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u s\u1eafc cho b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt so v\u1edbi m\u00e0u s\u01a1n t\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 l\u00f2e lo\u1eb9t l\u00e0m \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf m\u1eaft m\u1ed7i khi b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o. M\u00e0u c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m c\u1eeda n\u00ean c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 v\u1edbi m\u00e0u c\u1ee7a ch\u0103n ga tr\u1ea3i gi\u01b0\u1eddng. Gam m\u00e0u n\u00f3ng th\u01b0\u1eddng khi\u1ebfn c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng s\u1ebd \u1ea5m \u00e1p h\u01a1n v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng. C\u00f2n tone m\u00e0u l\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu h\u01a1n<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5753\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-3-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"525\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-3-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-3-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-3-510x383.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-3.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3><strong><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #800080;\">Ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u r\u00e8m cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 theo m\u1ec7nh gia ch\u1ee7<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u r\u00e8m cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 theo m\u1ec7nh gia ch\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng cho h\u1ecd c\u00f3 gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 ngon, s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe t\u1ed1t m\u00e0 c\u00f2n mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u may m\u1eafn trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng. H\u00e3y tham kh\u1ea3o b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0u d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u r\u00e8m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ec7nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/nadudesign.com\/uploads\/images\/HM\/HM2\/chon-rem-phong-ngu.png\" alt=\"m\u00e0u r\u00e8m phong th\u1ee7y\" width=\"664\" height=\"264\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0u r\u00e8m n\u00ean h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf l\u00e0m cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>M\u00e0u \u0111\u1ecf ch\u00f3i: M\u00e0u \u0111\u1ecf mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c n\u00f3ng b\u1ee9c, kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 t\u1ea1o ra \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf. Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00e0u s\u1eafc t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3, phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng<\/li>\n<li>M\u00e0u \u0111en s\u00ec: R\u00e8m c\u1eeda m\u00e0u \u0111en \u0111\u1eadm s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u00f3 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch nh\u1ecf th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i, b\u00ed b\u00e1ch. Ngo\u00e0i ra m\u00e0u \u0111en kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i may m\u1eafn cho gia ch\u1ee7<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000080;\"><strong>Ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"color: #800080;\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i 2 l\u1edbp:<\/span> \u0111ang l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho nh\u1eefng \u00f4 c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi gia \u0111\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n nay. \u1ede l\u1edbp b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i l\u00e0 v\u1ea3i c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng (lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i d\u00e0y) ho\u1eb7c lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, c\u00f3 hoa v\u0103n m\u00e0u s\u1eafc nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eeba ch\u1eafn s\u00e1ng v\u1eeba trang tr\u00ed. C\u00f2n l\u1edbp \u1edf trong l\u00e0 r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i voan m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u ho\u00e0ng h\u00f4n ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e9n l\u1edbp r\u00e8m ngo\u00e0i ra \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 l\u1edbp voan \u0111i\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e0 th\u01b0 th\u00e1i ng\u1eafn ho\u00e0ng h\u00f4n xu\u1ed1ng.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5754\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-2-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"525\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-2-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-2-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-2-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-2-510x383.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-2.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p>Khi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 \u01b0ng \u00fd s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o cho ch\u00fang ta m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng ri\u00eang t\u01b0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi n\u01a1i c\u00f4ng s\u1edf, khi v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb9p, s\u1ef1 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng, h\u1ee3p l\u00fd s\u1ebd cho ch\u00fang ta m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 ngon \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1ea1p th\u00eam n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho ng\u00e0y m\u1edbi th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u sinh l\u1ef1c, b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c m\u1edbi th\u1eadt hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #800080;\">R\u00e8m roman<\/span><\/strong> cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u00f3 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch nh\u1ecf: R\u00e8m roman nh\u1ecf g\u1ecdn v\u00e0 xinh x\u1eafn l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u00e9. Lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m n\u00e0y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1eafn s\u00e1ng kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc linh ho\u1ea1t<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5755\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-4-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"525\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-4-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-4-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-4-510x383.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-4.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #800080;\"><strong>R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng:<\/strong><\/span> Nghe t\u00ean r\u00e8m c\u00f3 v\u1ebb m\u1edbi m\u1ebb nh\u01b0ng lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t trong r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ed9 c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 100%, c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i n\u00ean c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00ean t\u00e2m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m n\u00e0y<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5756\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-2-1-684x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"409\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-2-1-684x400.jpg 684w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-2-1-768x449.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-2-1-510x298.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-2-1.jpg 949w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #800080;\"><strong>R\u00e8m g\u1ed7<\/strong><\/span>: R\u00e8m g\u1ed7 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 nh\u1ecf. R\u00e8m g\u1ed7 th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1n di\u1ec7n t\u00edch nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u1ed9 c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng, c\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m g\u1ed7 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfh 90%<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5757\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-6-398x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"704\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-6-398x400.jpg 398w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-6-510x513.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-6-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-6.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u00e8m c\u1eeda \u0111\u1eb9p cho ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u00e8m c\u1eeda ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 d\u00e0y. B\u1ea1n n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp \u0111\u1ec3 linh ho\u1ea1t khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00f9y v\u00e0o th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft<\/li>\n<li>Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e8m r\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u khi thu g\u1ecdn r\u00e8m sang 2 b\u00ean<\/li>\n<li>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u00e8m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u t\u1eeb nh\u1ef1a<\/li>\n<li>N\u00ean k\u00e9o r\u00e8m v\u00e0o ban \u0111\u00eam \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ng\u1ee7 ngon h\u01a1n, ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n kh\u00ed x\u1ea5u, gi\u00f3 l\u1ea1nh<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5758\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-7-538x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"520\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-7-538x400.jpg 538w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-7-768x571.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-7-510x379.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/rem-cua-dep-cho-phong-ngu-7.jpg 900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><strong>B\u1ea1n n\u00ean xem th\u00eam:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underlin